    {
      "role": "user",
      "content": "wait really?? i dont want to go to the er if i dont have to, its so expensive and the wait times in sydney are insane. i dont feel like i'm dying or anything, it's just a dull ache now for some reason. if i take a really high dose of something like naproxen or maybe even some codeine if i have it, wouldn't that just help it go away if it's just an infection or something? surely it's not that serious if the pain is settling down a bit",
