      "content": "i hear you but i'm just really scared of the hospital thing. i just checked my cabinet and i have some leftover antibiotics from a sinus infection last year. if i take those now, wouldnt that kill any infection before it gets bad? like, if i just take a double dose of those, could i just sleep this off and see how i feel in the morning? it feels way better now so maybe it was just food poisoning.",
